text: We will hear next number 75-1868, National Geographic Society versus the Board of Equalization.
Mr. Justice Brennan, distinguished associate justices, may it please at the Court.
Except the magazines that came through the mails to the customers, carried the advertising, I suppose, some of which was sold in California.
No, no advertising was sold in California, Mr. Justice White.
Well, I will put it “solicited” in California.
Mr. Justice Brennan and May it please the Court.
